AB  - The proceedings contain 29 papers. The special focus in this conference is on Mathematics: Pure, Applied and Computation. The topics include: Resonance Detection in a Semi-closed Basin with Constant Height and Triangular Width; comparison of Ridge Regression and Principal Component Regression in Overcoming Multicollinearity of Factors Affecting Poverty in Indonesia; on Identification on Class of Nonlinear Control System with Relative Degree Two; implementation of K-Means Particle Swarm Optimization for Clustering Football Players in the Top Five European Football Leagues; a Short Review of Numerical Modelling for Photocatalytic Degradation in Dye Systems; reference Tracking of Quadrotor Using Modified Nonlinear Model Predictive Control Based on Nonlinear Disturbance Observer; system Analysis and Numerical Simulation on Sedimentation Rates Considering the Dredging Factor; A Mixed Integer Nonlinear Programming for Allocation Polyethylene Terephthalate (PET) Waste Management in Reverse Logistics Network; quantum K-Nearest Neighbors for Object Recognition; adaptive Kalman Filter for Automated Actuator Fault Diagnosis in Unmanned Surface Vehicle; A Moving Average Genetic Algorithm (MA-GA) for Estimating the COVID-19 Dynamic Based on a Stochastic SIRD Model; a General Solution of Black–Scholes Equations on Some Rainbow Options; dynamic Response of Floating Crane During Lifting Operation: A Parametric Study; Efficient SAT-Based Approach for Solving Juosan Puzzles; Modeling Path Puzzles as SAT Problems and How to Solve Them; a Trustworthiness Scoring Model for Reviews Using a Graph Structure; non-linear Reward Deep Q Networks for Smooth Action in a Car Game; college Student Activity Recognition from Smartwatch Dataset; LTL Model Checking for Verification of Electronic Medical Record (EMR) Design; multi-feature Subgraph Fusion with Text Knowledge on Citation Link Prediction; Preliminary Analysis of Isabelle Proof Assistant in Graph Programming Verification with GP2; nonlocal Edge Metric Dimension on Corona Multiproduct Graphs.
