TI  - Molecular Control of Triplet-Pair Spin Polarization and Its Optoelectronic Magnetic Resonance Probes
LA  - eng
JF  - Accounts of Chemical Research
VL  - 57
IS  - 1
SP  - 59
EP  - 69
PY  - 2024
SN  - 15204898, 00014842
PB  - American Chemical Society
