TI  - In silicoprediction of annihilators for triplet-triplet annihilation upconversionviaauxiliary-field quantum Monte Carlo
LA  - eng
JF  - Chemical Science
VL  - 12
IS  - 3
SP  - 1068
EP  - 1079
PY  - 2021
