TI  - Old school techniques with modern capabilities: Kinetics determination of dynamical information such as barriers, multiple entrance channel complexes, product states, spin crossings, and size effects in metallic ion-molecule reactions
LA  - eng
JF  - Journal of Physical Chemistry a
