TI  - Self-organized resource allocation based on traffic prediction for load imbalance in HetNets with NOMA
LA  - eng
A2  - Lei Wang, Tie Qiu, Wenbing Zhao
JF  - Lecture Notes of the Institute for Computer Sciences, Social-informatics and Telecommunications Engineering, Lnicst
VL  - 234
