AB  - The highest oxidation states of the transition metal fluorides are discussed along with their oxidizing power. The most powerful oxidizing agents will be presented and ranked in relation to each other. In conjunction, every d-block element is reported with its characteristic properties as well as its preparation route. Possible new high potential oxidizers are introduced based on quantum chemical predictions.
